-------------------------
            LAB 1
     (Network Scanning)
-------------------------
nmap -sn 10.10.x.x
nmap -sS 10.10.x.x
nmap -sV 10.10.x.x
nmap -O 10.10.x.x
nmap -p- 10.10.x.x
nmap -A 10.10.x.x



-------------------------
            LAB 3
       (IDS - Suricata)
-------------------------
sudo suricata -i eth0
tail -f /var/log/suricata/fast.log



-------------------------
            LAB 4
      (Firewall - UFW)
-------------------------
sudo ufw enable
sudo ufw allow ssh
sudo ufw deny 80
sudo ufw status numbered
sudo ufw delete <number>



-------------------------
            LAB 6
   (Social Engineering Toolkit)
-------------------------
sudo setoolkit
# → Social-Engineering Attacks
# → Website Attack Vectors
# → Credential Harvester
# → Enter attacker IP + website URL



-------------------------
            LAB 7
       (Autopsy Forensics)
-------------------------
1. Create New Case
2. Add Data Source → Disk Image (.E01/.dd)
3. Select image file
4. Configure Ingest → Select All (except Plaso)
5. Analyze findings:
   - OS Accounts
   - Browser History
   - Recent Activity
   - Deleted Files
   - Hash Values
6. Export evidence (optional)
7. Generate Report (optional)



